      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This exceptional vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning buyer. Meticulously maintained and demonstrating consistent performance, it offers a refined driving experience and proven mechanical reliability. With its well-preserved interior and robust powertrain, this automobile stands as a testament to quality care and responsible ownership. We invite you to experience the sophistication and dependable engineering of this distinguished model.",
      "price": 34900.0,
